thread.title_full: SecurCare Self Storage reviewed by Nancy

author: Nancy
title: Nancy
text: I went and got my storage unit and everything has went pretty well. I purchased my unit over the phone and everything was simple and quick. The next day I went in signed some papers and after 10-15 minutes i was moving things in. The customer service was great. The lady that helped me at the front desk was very nice. Place is clean and I have to say havent had no problems.
